            "voiceover": [
                "The Bleed Fixer adjusts the bleed boxes of your PDF for proper printing.",
                "Open the PDF in the Editor and click the Bleed Fix button.",
                "Enter the desired bleed size (default 3 mm) and optionally preserve the crop box.",
                "Apply the correction and download the updated PDF."
            ]
        },
